The [[Pakuuni Pirates]] used [[Class-A cargo container|Container]] '''''CRM908A''''' as a storage container during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. As part of an expansion project, [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces, left by [[Grand Admiral/Legends|Grand Admiral]] [[Mitth'raw'nuruodo/Legends|Thrawn]] raided a Pakuuni Pirate outpost during the [[Battle on the Frontier]]. Imperial [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] destroyed as many Pakuuni vessels as possible, along with any cargo vessels in the area, including containers from group ''CRM908A''. [[Maarek Stele/Legends|Maarek Stele]], present at the battle, inspected the cargo containers prior to their destruction, locating [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] onboard. [[Nebulon-B2 frigate]] ''[[Ludwick]]'' dispatched [[Gamma-class ATR-6 assault transport|Assault Transport]] [[Tiger (Gamma-class ATR-6 assault transport)|''Tiger'']] to capture the Rebels, afterward Imperial [[TIE/sa tactical bomber/Legends|TIE Bombers]] destroyed the remaining container.

